      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLAMIN' JOE (4) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Scored over 340m at this track last time in a Grade 4/5 (18.96). Has never missed the frame here at the trip from eight starts. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to go well again. ZIPPING ZEPPELIN (1) goes very well at the distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Missed the frame latest (18.41) when fourth over 320m at Richmond in a NG. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. JET LINKIN (8) has a strong record this trip with 10 wins and 10 placings from 29 starts. Placed last time (19.97) at Goulburn in a NG, finishing second and beaten 4.5 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. MAGIC LINKIN (2) is always a threat when he races at this journey.",
